node.text: Cable Clamp Cover™️ Eliminate your stolen charging cables right at the source. This revolutionary outlet cover features our signature locking technology to secure your charging brick and cable directly into your wall for safe keeping. Simply slide your cable through our passthrough port, insert your USB brick into the sure fit pocket, and screw the entire cover into your outlet to finally stop the steal of your most prized possession. #unnecessaryinventions

node.text: The Zoom-ouflage Shirt™️ Create the illusion you are fully dressed on your next Zoom call. This mini mannequin is perfect for all those days you simply don’t want to get dressed. Strategically place it in front of your computer’s WebCam to undoubtedly fool every person you encounter digitally. Enjoy your day in absolute nature comfort… just don’t stand up! (Concept submitted by @jonnyox) #unnecessaryinventions

node.text: The Slice Slapper™️ Eliminate horrible pizza toppings in an instant! Our debut removal tool features an easy push button and tri-angled blades to rapidly chop away any potion of your pizza pie featuring ingredients you would NEVER eat. Simply locate the deplorable section and slap it away to customize your pizza to your unique one of a kind taste. Now… who TF ordered the pineapple olive mushroom pizza?!? (Idea submitted by @josepinto1301) #unnecessaryinventions

Now unleash your rage in any direction with full peace of mind. #unnecessaryinventions

node.text: The Cob Quicky™️ Hands down the easiest way to butter your corn on the cob. With our  latest offering, grab yourself a fresh stick of butter go to town on your cob. Simply insert the butter on to our firm grip center spikes and slather your corn from top to bottom.  It’s time to show off your go to technique at your next BBQ. Are you a righty or lefty? #unnecessaryinventions

node.text: The Drink O’Clock™️ Is it time for a cocktail yet?! Our revolutionary 24 hour clock ditches the idea of knowing the exact specific time by simply letting you know what to drink. If you aren’t quite sure the progress of the day simply glance at this clock for a thirst quenching reminder if it’s time to drink coffee or time to drink alcohol. Then again it’s 5 o’clock somewhere! #unnecessaryinventions

node.text: The Cruise N Breeze™️ No Air Conditioning, No problem. Our never before seen device funnels the outdoor air through the distinctive S-curve tube directly into your car to keep you at the perfect temperature. The ballistic netting will ensure no bugs or debris will enter your vehicle while in motion. The faster you go the stronger the force of air! It’s never been more simple to stay cool for the summer. #unnecessaryinventions
